PREFACE TO THE FIRST EDITION.

THIS book is sent forth as the best attempt at an Edi- tion of the Pro Murena that with short time and pressing College engagements I can make. Being familiar with the speech from frequent reading, and having collected matter upon many passages myself, I have taken the best authorities as guides in the writing of noteS, and striven to give brief but full acknowledgment for what I have borrowed from them.
